# Line-ending normalization (added 2026-07-20).
# Repo stores LF; checkout is LF on all platforms. Ends the CRLF/LF churn caused
# by core.autocrlf=true with no attributes, which made Windows-authored files —
# especially _bmad-output/baseline-report/* — show as perpetually "modified" and
# littered every commit with "LF will be replaced by CRLF" warnings. LF also
# matches the Linux CI runners + the VPS, so there is one consistent form.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize (would corrupt them).
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.gif   binary
*.ico   binary
*.webp  binary
*.svg   text eol=lf
*.pdf   binary
*.xlsx  binary
*.xls   binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf   binary
*.eot   binary
*.zip   binary
*.gz    binary
